  "description": "¶Pushed Propaganda A couple days ago, I was washing the dishes or cleaning the counters or something, when my phone sent me a push notification from Substack. This notification was from a white settler anarchist who\u0026rsquo;s partners with a different white settler anarchist whose Substack I subscribe to. Substack does that, whenever I start posting on it more: sends me updates about what\u0026rsquo;s happening past the edge of my network.\n",
